SUMMARY:Oral Method's Vernal
DESCRIPTION:Oral Method\, in partnership with Factory Theatre\, presents: Vernal. Join us for an evening of new writing\, experimental writing!  \n\n\n\nFriday\, March 20 | Doors: 7PM | Readings: 7:30PM \n\n\n\nFactory Theatre\, 125 Bathurst St\, Toronto \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nAlex Ateah \n\n\n\nAriella Garmaise \n\n\n\nKnowah Holder \n\n\n\nStephen Jackman-Torkoff \n\n\n\nErum Khan \n\n\n\nAliya Pabani \n\n\n\nfeat. Simone Hogeveen and Wendi Jiang \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nOrganized by Kalale Dalton-Lutale and Esmé Hogeveen with support from the Toronto Arts Council \n\n\n\nPoster by Maddie Kingston \n\n\n\n\nBOOK TICKETS
URL:https://www.factorytheatre.ca/event/oral-methods-vernal/
CATEGORIES:Rentals
END:VEVENT
